  "body": "<p>We love seeing you all using Amy Tangerine products in a variety of projects. Here are some that we have spotted being used in Project Life. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600127886133-VDXCIK3FJXW0WDQ6XQJE/7a-6a00d8345260b569e20177436cb8da970d-900wi-600x392.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.jamaicamakes.com/jamaica/2012/07/crapload-of-thickers.html\">By Jamaica Edgell</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600127930422-DOL4TJ4U87EXTUA5WZLJ/7b-IMG_1058_2-1-600x399.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://michellewooderson.blogspot.com/2012/07/project-life-week-21-2012keeping-it.html\">By Michelle Wooderson</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600127990823-UN9EE206EW0DF0IP7B5I/7c-sony-dsc-143-600x579.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://documentingchaos.com/2012/07/10/project-life-week-27/\">By Sarah</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600128025385-2ZX164TMOOUS0851MD47/7d-6a00d8341c71c353ef017ee55622d2970d.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://eliseblaha.typepad.com/golden/2012/11/project-life-week-46.html\">By Elise Blaha</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600128055334-2FQ4IF4AFIXW6X5O7S6V/7e-AE_PL2012_WK25_left-600x546.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://aliedwards.com/2012/07/project-life-week-twenty-five-2.html\">By Ali Edwards</a> </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>You can get our products online at <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabuc